&lt;li data-start=&quot;936&quot; data-end=&quot;1031&quot;&gt;Facilitate all Scrum ceremonies including daily stand-ups, sprint planning, backlog&amp;nbsp;grooming, sprint reviews, and retrospectives&lt;/li&gt;
